OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,FITV News London joined survivors and
OL,7,Fthose who have suffered loss from
OL,8,FLondon to the Big Apple, following
OL,9,Ftheir personal journey.
OL,11,FThe play ends on the street under the
OL,12,FBrooklyn Bridge, where actors interact
OL,13,Fwith US theatre-goers to hear what
OL,14,Fthey think about the US company
OL,15,Fselling it's banned cladding to the UK
OL,16,Fmarket.
OL,18,F"We just want to say, I'm thinking of
OL,19,Fjoining our community this evening,"
OL,20,Fsays one of the actors, as the curtain
OL,21,Ffalls on the production.
