OL,6,FThe audience and actors move out of
OL,7,Fthe theater and onto the street.
OL,9,F"Not only for the people of Grenfell,
OL,10,Fbut every single person around the
OL,11,Fworld who is being failed by the
OL,12,Fsystem. Thank you so much," the actor
OL,13,Ffinishes.
OL,15,FMembers of the audience across the
OL,16,Fpond feel the Grenfell story resonates
OL,17,Fin America, "Grenfell in its way, is
OL,18,FLondon's 9/11 story. So of course it
OL,19,Fwill resonate with New Yorkers,"
