OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,FThe documentary play about Grenfell is
OL,7,Fopening at New York's St Ann's
OL,8,FWarehouse theatre. Grenfell, in the
OL,9,Fwords of survivors, tells the story of
OL,10,Fthe fire before, during and after the
OL,11,Ftragedy that killed 72 people.
OL,13,FIt first opened last year at the
OL,14,FNational Theatre and its transferred
OL,15,Fto Brooklyn exposes the same safety
OL,16,Ffailures and absence of any criminal
OL,17,Fconvictions seven years on.
