OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,FBehind the curtain in Grenfell tragedy
OL,7,Fis an American company, Arconic. The
OL,8,Fmakers of the deadly cladding that
OL,9,Fcover the tower and help spread the
OL,10,Ffire and their headquarters are
OL,11,Fsituated in New York's neighboring
OL,12,Fstate of Pennsylvania.
OL,14,FJumaane Williams is a New York
OL,15,Fpolitician invited to watch the
OL,16,FGrenfell play and talk about the
OL,17,Ftragedy.
OL,19,FHe believes more Americans should know
OL,20,Fabout Arconic and the dangerous
OL,21,Fcladding they sold.
