OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,F"I mean, it's disgusting. They very
OL,7,Fclearly decided to sell it in markets
OL,8,Fthat they knew they could, even though
OL,9,Fthey knew that was dangerous.
OL,11,FThere should be penalties for that,
OL,12,Fand I think if the U.S. is really an
OL,13,Fally, they would do something about it.
OL,15,FThere has to be pressure put on
OL,16,Fcompanies who kill folks," he said.
OL,18,FChris Ivey is an activist filmmaker
OL,19,Fwho lives in Pittsburgh, home to
OL,20,FArconic headquarters.
