OL,6,F"It's frustrating for me knowing that
OL,7,Fthey felt safe being in Pittsburgh by
OL,8,Fdoing all this harm in the U.K., you
OL,9,Fknow, I think is horrible.
OL,11,F"And they always talk about it, it's
OL,12,Falways about profit over people."
OL,14,FNew York is a city of tall towers, but
OL,15,Fnone had arconic cladding.
OL,17,FIt was deemed too dangerous to sell in
OL,18,FAmerica, something not lost on
OL,19,Fplaywright Gillian Slovo, "our
OL,20,Fgovernment didn't stop them from
OL,21,Fselling it to us either.
