OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,F"I do think it is very important that
OL,7,Fpeople here also realise the effect an
OL,8,FAmerican company is having on other
OL,9,Fcountries and other people's lives,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FThe play is a critical hit in New
OL,13,FYork, getting rave reviews as well as
OL,14,Fcelebrity endorsements. Sarah Jessica
OL,15,FParker watched the performance and
OL,16,Fcalled it "monumental" and said that
OL,17,F"the tragedy should never be
OL,18,Fforgotten," on social media.
