OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,FAlso in New York, one of the real
OL,7,Fplayers in this tragedy is Edward
OL,8,FDaffarn, who escaped from the 16th
OL,9,Ffloor of the tower.
OL,11,FHe said, "my main hope from this visit
OL,12,Fwith the play is that we will have
OL,13,Freached an American audience who now
OL,14,Funderstands that although Grenfell
OL,15,Fhappened a long way away, actually,
OL,16,Fsome of the causes of Grenfell started
OL,17,Fright here in their own backyards."
