OL,6,FIn the Grenfell stage version, he's
OL,7,Fplayed by the actor Michael Shaeffer,
OL,8,Fwho told ITV News London, "there is a
OL,9,Fhope that by making this kind of an
OL,10,Finternational conversation, if you
OL,11,Flike, the shame that should be there
OL,12,Ffor the British government is
OL,13,Fheightened because this story is now
OL,14,Fbeing told across the pond."
OL,16,F"It's being told in the Big Apple. So
OL,17,Fhopefully that means that the stink is
OL,18,Flouder."
