OL,3,C'London's 9/11': Grenfell survivors
OL,4,Ctake play to the streets of New York
OL,6,FThe production is making the right
OL,7,Fnoises stateside, but almost seven
OL,8,Fyears have passed since the fire, and
OL,9,Flike the play, the Grenfell story is
OL,10,Fone that's still waiting for its
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Arconic said:
OL,14,F"Since this tragedy occurred, our
OL,15,Fthoughts have been, and remain with
OL,16,Fthose who lost their lives, the
OL,17,Fsurvivors, and their families. As we
OL,18,Fawait the publication of the report
OL,19,Ffollowing the latest phase of the
OL,20,FInquiry it would not be appropriate to
OL,21,Fadd further comment."
